38-2889.Delegated dispensing permit; advisory committees; authorized.

The board may appoint formulary advisory committees as deemed necessary for the determination of formularies for delegated dispensing permittees.

SourceLaws 1994, LB 900, § 29;Laws 1996, LB 1044, § 469;Laws 1998, LB 1073, § 82;Laws 2001, LB 398, § 63;R.S.1943, (2003), § 71-1,147.59;Laws 2007, LB296, § 354;Laws 2007, LB463, § 985;Laws 2009, LB154, § 7.
